headline: Lamb Weston Holdings Announces Quarterly Dividend
summary: EAGLE, Idaho, July 15, 2025--The Board of Directors of Lamb Weston Holdings, Inc. (NYSE: LW) today declared a quarterly dividend of $0.37 per share of Lamb Weston common stock. The dividend is payable on August 29, 2025, to stockholders of record as of the close of business on August 1, 2025.
